  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] yeah, I really think that the way-- the best way for me to describe this-- this nightmare is that it was all of one big macabre dance of death that we were all dancing, some unconsciously and some consciously, or more consciously than others.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it was really just a-- a dance of death.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Did the average resident in the ghetto have access to outside of the ghetto?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Who at that time was patrolling external-- externally?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was all the Hungarian gendarme.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, to the best of my recollection, and although I have learned since then that [INAUDIBLE] apparently had with it at Kisvarda once, there was one young SS man who was guiding, directing, and maybe even commanding the local gendarme.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But they really needed very little guidance, or very little help.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Hungarian gendarme really was a particularly brutal and-- and [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] what do you call it?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Aggressive and-- and wild institution from its very inception.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were in charge, for all intents and purposes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] To what extent they were guided by-- bye the Germans is-- is something that I-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But as I say, they needed very little guidance.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Interestingly enough, one of the-- the plans we hatched, the-- the-- the other side of the ghetto or-- or of Star Street, the end of where the Jewish school was-- just behind the Jewish school was, and that was all part of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were about 12,000 people in the ghetto in Kisvarda, so you can imagine, they were all squeezed into, I would say, within the equivalent of in-- in built up area, of about two blocks.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe three, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
